        "timestamp": "2018-09-07 21:08:53.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 15: Code-Review+2\n\nI had K8s Env. issues and was heavily delayed today!\n\nAnyhow, I removed the AAI chart, updated the chart and then deployed it again and things came up.  There was one issue that I have found with the removal of AAI and a few other charts.  The way you've done the PVC claim within the statefulset leaves the PVC objects dangling after a helm del aai --purge....so it never fully cleans itself up properly.  Any subsequent helm install to put it back will fail because the PVC already exists....  We will have to fix that dangling PVC issue or have steps to remove them manually.\n\n\nBasic A&AI Health Check                                               | PASS |",
        "patchset_number": 15
