        "message": "Patch Set 15:\n\n@Mandeep, I tried looking into helm and why its not removing the pvc and it seems that helm for some reason doesn't remove the PVC. I will try to investigate further, if we can't find a way to remove the PVC as part of cleanup then we need to document that. Would we just update the README and wiki or anywhere else?",
